#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. Rule"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Kassakasutta"
msgstr "19. A Farmer"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn4.19:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā bhikkhūnaṃ nibbānapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā "
"kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the Buddha was educating, encouraging, firing up, and "
"inspiring the mendicants with a Dhamma talk about extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn4.19:1.3"
msgid ""
"Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā "
"dhammaṃ suṇanti."
msgstr ""
"And those mendicants were paying heed, paying attention, engaging "
"wholeheartedly, and lending an ear."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.115"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.255"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho mārassa pāpimato etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Māra thought:"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.2"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo bhikkhūnaṃ nibbānapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""
"“The ascetic Gotama is giving a Dhamma talk about extinguishment … and the "
"mendicants are listening well."

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.3"
msgid "yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ vicakkhukammāyā”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I go and pull the wool over their eyes?”"

# BB has a typo here.
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā kassakavaṇṇaṃ abhinimminitvā mahantaṃ naṅgalaṃ khandhe "
"karitvā dīghapācanayaṭṭhiṃ gahetvā haṭahaṭakeso sāṇasāṭinivattho "
"kaddamamakkhitehi pādehi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked manifested in the form of a farmer carrying a large "
"plough on his shoulder. He held a long goad, his hair was messy, he was clad "
"in sunn hemp, and his feet were muddy. He went up to the Buddha and said to "
"him:"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.5"
msgid "“api, samaṇa, balībadde addasā”ti?"
msgstr "“So, ascetic, did you happen to see any oxen?”"

# A genuinely interesting question. Mara and oxen: what’s up with that?
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.6"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, pāpima, te balībaddehī”ti?"
msgstr "“But what have you to do with oxen, Wicked One?”"

# Despite BB’s note, I think it’s unlikely that Mara was familiar with 5th century abhidhamma. If the phrase here means anything, it’s more likely to represent Mara’s clumsiness and confusion.
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.7"
msgid "“Mameva, samaṇa, cakkhu, mama rūpā, mama cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mine alone, ascetic, is the eye, mine are sights, mine is the field of eye "
"contact consciousness."

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.8"
msgid "Kuhiṃ me, samaṇa, gantvā mokkhasi?"
msgstr "Where can you escape me, ascetic?"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.9"
msgid "Mameva, samaṇa, sotaṃ, mama saddā … pe …"
msgstr "Mine alone is the ear …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.10"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, ghānaṃ, mama gandhā;"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.11"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, jivhā, mama rasā;"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.12"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, kāyo, mama phoṭṭhabbā;"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.13"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, mano, mama dhammā, mama manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"mind, mine are thoughts, mine is the field of mind contact consciousness."

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.14"
msgid "Kuhiṃ me, samaṇa, gantvā mokkhasī”ti?"
msgstr "Where can you escape me, ascetic?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.116"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.256"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:3.1"
msgid "“Taveva, pāpima, cakkhu, tava rūpā, tava cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Yours alone, ascetic, is the eye, yours are sights, yours is the field of "
"eye contact consciousness."

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi cakkhu, natthi rūpā, natthi "
"cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima."
msgstr ""
"Where there is no eye, no sights, no eye contact consciousness—you have no "
"place there, Wicked One!"

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.3"
msgid "Taveva, pāpima, sotaṃ, tava saddā, tava sotasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr "Yours alone is the ear …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi sotaṃ, natthi saddā, natthi "
"sotasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.5"
msgid "Taveva, pāpima, ghānaṃ, tava gandhā, tava ghānasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.6"
msgid ""
"Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi ghānaṃ, natthi gandhā, natthi "
"ghānasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.7"
msgid ""
"Taveva, pāpima, jivhā, tava rasā, tava jivhāsamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.8"
msgid ""
"taveva, pāpima, kāyo, tava phoṭṭhabbā, tava kāyasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ … pe "
"…"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.9"
msgid "taveva, pāpima, mano, tava dhammā, tava manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"mind, yours are thoughts, yours is the field of mind contact consciousness."

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.10"
msgid ""
"Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi mano, natthi dhammā, natthi "
"manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpimā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Where there is no mind, no thoughts, no mind contact consciousness—you have "
"no place there, Wicked One!”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ vadanti mama yidanti,"
msgstr "“The things they call ‘mine’,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.2"
msgid "ye vadanti mamanti ca;"
msgstr "and those who say ‘it’s mine’:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.3"
msgid "Ettha ce te mano atthi,"
msgstr "if your mind remains there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti."
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ vadanti na taṃ mayhaṃ,"
msgstr "“The things they speak of aren’t mine;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.2"
msgid "ye vadanti na te ahaṃ;"
msgstr "I’m not someone who speaks like that."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ pāpima jānāhi,"
msgstr "So know this, Wicked One:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.4"
msgid "na me maggampi dakkhasī”ti."
msgstr "you won’t even see the path I take.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.19:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."
